 <notes>* Fixed recurring weekly events with fixed number of occurences
  but multiple incidences per week (kolab/issue3846)
* Fixed recurring weekly events with intervals > 1 (Bug #8546)
* Added Horde_Date_Recurrence class.
* Add PHP 4 fallback for mktime and dates outside of 1970-2038.
* Correctly match dates with T/Z splitters (Request #4267).
* Added weekOfMonth() (Request #5229).
* Fixed broken time format generators.
</notes>
